        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="行测学习-Day06"><a href="#行测学习-Day06" class="headerlink" title="行测学习 Day06"></a>行测学习 Day06</h2><h3 id="一-学习内容"><a href="#一-学习内容" class="headerlink" title="一. 学习内容"></a>一. 学习内容</h3><p>增长倍数</p><p>间隔增长率：r = $r_1$ + $r_2$ + $r_1$ * $r_2$</p><p>混合增长率：线段法</p><h3 id="二-增长倍数"><a href="#二-增长倍数" class="headerlink" title="二. 增长倍数"></a>二. 增长倍数</h3><h4 id="倍数与增长率"><a href="#倍数与增长率" class="headerlink" title="倍数与增长率"></a>倍数与增长率</h4><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/yangqifeng01/picture/blog/20230309093510.png" alt="20230309093510"></p><h4 id="求基期增长倍数（基期增长率）"><a href="#求基期增长倍数（基期增长率）" class="headerlink" title="求基期增长倍数（基期增长率）"></a>求基期增长倍数（基期增长率）</h4><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/yangqifeng01/picture/blog/20230309093651.png" alt="20230309093651"></p><h3 id="三-间隔增长率"><a href="#三-间隔增长率" class="headerlink" title="三. 间隔增长率"></a>三. 间隔增长率</h3><h4 id="题型识别与解法"><a href="#题型识别与解法" class="headerlink" title="题型识别与解法"></a>题型识别与解法</h4><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/yangqifeng01/picture/blog/20230309093923.png" alt="20230309093923"></p><h4 id="间隔倍数"><a href="#间隔倍数" class="headerlink" title="间隔倍数"></a>间隔倍数</h4><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/yangqifeng01/picture/blog/20230309094018.png" alt="20230309094018"></p><h4 id="间隔基期量"><a href="#间隔基期量" class="headerlink" title="间隔基期量"></a>间隔基期量</h4><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/yangqifeng01/picture/blog/20230309094117.png" alt="20230309094117"></p><h3 id="四-年均增长率"><a href="#四-年均增长率" class="headerlink" title="四. 年均增长率"></a>四. 年均增长率</h3><h4 id="题型识别与公式"><a href="#题型识别与公式" class="headerlink" title="题型识别与公式"></a>题型识别与公式</h4><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/yangqifeng01/picture/blog/20230309094323.png" alt="20230309094323"></p><h4 id="解法"><a href="#解法" class="headerlink" title="解法"></a>解法</h4><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/yangqifeng01/picture/blog/20230309094410.png" alt="20230309094410"></p><h4 id="常考平方数"><a href="#常考平方数" class="headerlink" title="常考平方数"></a>常考平方数</h4><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/yangqifeng01/picture/blog/20230309095224.png" alt="20230309095224"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/yangqifeng01/picture/blog/20230309094517.png" alt="20230309094517"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/yangqifeng01/picture/blog/20230309094540.png" alt="20230309094540"></p><h3 id="五-混合增长率"><a href="#五-混合增长率" class="headerlink" title="五. 混合增长率"></a>五. 混合增长率</h3><h4 id="线段法"><a href="#线段法" class="headerlink" title="线段法"></a>线段法</h4><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/yangqifeng01/picture/blog/20230309094810.png" alt="20230309094810"></p><h4 id="题型识别与解法-1"><a href="#题型识别与解法-1" class="headerlink" title="题型识别与解法"></a>题型识别与解法</h4><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/yangqifeng01/picture/blog/20230309094928.png" alt="20230309094928"></p><p><strong>基期量可以用现期量替代</strong></p>]]></content>
      
      
