        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="行测学习-Day05"><a href="#行测学习-Day05" class="headerlink" title="行测学习 Day05"></a>行测学习 Day05</h2><h3 id="一-学习内容"><a href="#一-学习内容" class="headerlink" title="一. 学习内容"></a>一. 学习内容</h3><p>比重：比重中的饼图问题，计算基期比重，两期比重<br>平均数：现期平均数，基期平均数，两期平均数的比较</p><h3 id="二-比重"><a href="#二-比重" class="headerlink" title="二. 比重"></a>二. 比重</h3><h4 id="饼图问题"><a href="#饼图问题" class="headerlink" title="饼图问题"></a>饼图问题</h4><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/yangqifeng01/picture/blog/20230307163230.png" alt="20230307163230"></p><h4 id="基期比重"><a href="#基期比重" class="headerlink" title="基期比重"></a>基期比重</h4><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/yangqifeng01/picture/blog/20230307163630.png" alt="20230307163630"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/yangqifeng01/picture/blog/20230307163414.png" alt="20230307163414"></p><p>精算化一法公式：**${A \over B} * (1 + {b-a \over 1+a})$**<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/yangqifeng01/picture/blog/20230307163750.png" alt="20230307163750"></p><h4 id="两期比重的比较–升降"><a href="#两期比重的比较–升降" class="headerlink" title="两期比重的比较–升降"></a>两期比重的比较–升降</h4><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/yangqifeng01/picture/blog/20230307164300.png" alt="20230307164300"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/yangqifeng01/picture/blog/20230307164414.png" alt="20230307164414"></p><h4 id="两期比重的计算"><a href="#两期比重的计算" class="headerlink" title="两期比重的计算"></a>两期比重的计算</h4><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/yangqifeng01/picture/blog/20230307164545.png" alt="20230307164545"></p><h3 id="三-平均数"><a href="#三-平均数" class="headerlink" title="三. 平均数"></a>三. 平均数</h3><h4 id="现期平均数"><a href="#现期平均数" class="headerlink" title="现期平均数"></a>现期平均数</h4><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/yangqifeng01/picture/blog/20230307164744.png" alt="20230307164744"></p><h4 id="基期平均数"><a href="#基期平均数" class="headerlink" title="基期平均数"></a>基期平均数</h4><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/yangqifeng01/picture/blog/20230307164917.png" alt="20230307164917"></p><h4 id="两期平均数"><a href="#两期平均数" class="headerlink" title="两期平均数"></a>两期平均数</h4><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/yangqifeng01/picture/blog/20230307165340.png" alt="20230307165340"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/yangqifeng01/picture/blog/20230307165428.png" alt="20230307165428"></p>]]></content>
      
      
